Requirements
    - python >= 2.5
    - python-simplejson
    - xmms2 with python support (tested against DrMattDestruction, it probably won't work with another DR version)

Building
    - no need to build

Running
    cd src
    python main.py
    then browse to http://localhost:8000/


You may report bugs to http://xmms2-httplay.googlecode.com/


Enjoy!
--
Simon Poirier

